title: TJ Bonnette from As Cities Burn
itunes:title: TJ Bonnette from As Cities Burn
description:
Happy Holidays everyone! We have a fun chat today with TJ Bonnette from As Cities Burn about him growing up in Louisiana, balancing priorities in life and staying creative. The band is definitely an interesting story and TJ is able to lay it all out for us! Enjoy and see you next year.
